#HOW TO
###MINIKUBE

Install minikube and start it


###Create namespace

cd cluster/specs/ns
k apply -f mongodb.yaml
k apply -f rabbitmq.yaml

cd cluster/specs/rabbit
k apply -f rabbitmq.yaml

cd cluster/specs/mongo-arm
k apply -f mongodb-arm.yaml

cd cluster/specs/mongo
k apply -f mongodb.yaml

### Apply secrets 
cd cluster/k && k apply -k mongo

cd cluster/k && k apply -k rabbit


